OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start for many,
OL,6,Falthough low cloud quickly burning
OL,7,Faway through the morning. A fine day
OL,8,Ffollows with warm sunny spells,
OL,9,Fespecially in the south, but also some
OL,10,Fpatchy higher cloud. Some lower cloud
OL,11,Fperhaps persisting along coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLight winds, with low cloud
OL,14,Fand coastal mist again spilling inland
OL,15,Ffrom the North Sea. Best of the clear
OL,16,Fspells in the west. Staying dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
