OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA similar day to Thursday,
OL,6,Fwith cloud clearing through the
OL,7,Fmorning, to give good sunny spells.
OL,8,FLikely feeling cooler due to a fresher
OL,9,Fnorth to northeasterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,12,Ffine and largely dry, with plenty of
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Skies remaining clearer
OL,14,Fovernight, with winds more generally
OL,15,Ffrom the north, perhaps brisk along
OL,16,Fcoasts on Saturday. Temperatures near
OL,17,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
